yeah, i'm kinda ready for all this to be over:

  • the-usless-gossip-over-heard-between-classes-from-peers-who's-existence-is-supurfolous
  • bitchy-power-hungry-hall-monitors-who-feel-the-need-to-exercise-their-dominence-on-highschool-student-in-order-to-feel-importantant-to-society
  • gym class1
  • life-controled-by-an-electronic-beep-that-goes-off-atleast-every-fourty-minutes
  • the listless apathetic feeling i wake up with everymonring
  • monotonous-rambling-of-intructural-educators-whom-you-know-is-unfit-to-teach-anyone2
  • guidence counselors helplessness

Who feels the same? Fell free to add your own and we'll get a nice little list going.

1This includes the lady that gets PAID to open the locker room door
2teachers

<center>Today I met the man of my dreams.
He came from heaven,
orderd a McChicken and walked out of my like,
<U>forever</U>.
